GNOME Utilities - "Of the Girl"
===============================================================================
Version: 3.0.0

GNOME Utilities for the GNOME 3.0 Desktop contains the following -

	gnome-system-log	[logview]
	gnome-search-tool	[gseachtool]
	gnome-dictionary	[gnome-dictionary]
	gnome-screenshot	[gnome-screenshot]
	baobab                  [baobab]
	font-viewer             [font-viewer]

Requirements -

	intltool	>= 0.40.0
	gnome-common	>= 2.3.0
	glib		>= 2.28.0
	gtk+            >= 3.0.3
	libgtop         >= 2.12.0
	gconf
        libcanberra-gtk3 >= 0.4


The following configure flags can be used -

  --enable-zlib                   Enable ZLib support for Logview [default=yes]
  --with-grep                     Specify the path to the grep
                                  command [default=find it ourselves]
  --enable-debug                  Enable debug messages [default=no]

Installation -

See the file 'INSTALL'

How to report bugs -

See the file 'BUGS'

How to contribute -

